ofs use ideas related to Witsenhausen's rate, OR graph products,\ncolorings of Cayley graphs and the chromatic numbers of Kneser graphs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jun 2008 17:42:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-06-20"}
